er/interact/102567/', '', 'Hydrochlorothiazide, Indapamide, Bisoprolol, Atorvastatin, Simvastatin, Lovastatin, Rosuvastatin, Pravastatin, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, Fenofibrate', 'Fesoterodine, Pentosan polysulfate, Calcium chloride, Phenazopyridine, Alprostadil, Trospium, Mirabegron, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Flavoxate, Darifenacin, More', 1767369485);
